      • withPattern

        public StorageBuilder withPattern​(java.lang.String pattern)
        Supply a pattern to fulfil this inventory. It will fetch all char and set an item according to the char. 'O' means nothing, it's equals to ' ' and indicates to skip this item index
        Parameters:
        pattern - a pattern String that is not empty
        Returns:
        this builder
        See Also:
        supplyPattern(char, Item)
